God deliver us from all venom of sin, by the inter­ cession and merits of Taurinus, the benignant bishop;
and shedding on us abundantly the perfect light of his holy vir­ tues, unite us to the company of his saints in the heavenly mansions, where we may worthily pour forth praises to the King of kings, through all ages.
